3D Scene Instruction Manual
Default Projection Mode is Perspective

################################
####        To build        ####
################################


    1. extract the folder hw7 from the hw7.zip
    2. run ~$ make && ./hw7



################################
####        Controls        ####
################################


////// CAMERA CONTROL //////////

Strafe Camera Left/Right
    A/a and D/d Keys
    
Move forward/backward
    W/w and S/s Keys 

Look Camera Up/Down:
    Up and Down Arrow Keys

Look Camera left/right
    Left and Right Arrow Keys


/////// LIGHT CONTROL ////////

Move light forward/backward
    G/g and B/b keys

Change elevation up and down
    e and E keys

/////////////////////////////////////////



Close the window
    ESC key
    
Reset View
    '0' key

Zoom out/in
    'z'/'x' keys

